<biogHist>
<abstract>The Metropolitan Charities Appeal Association was formed on 3 January 1918 at the instigation of the Ugly Men's Association to avoid 'the necessity for a score or more appeals for charities during the year'. It possibly was disbanded after July 1918.</abstract>

</biogHist>
